  "body": "From packages like `runtime, runtime/debug` we could expose go default metrics like:\r\n* `go_info`\r\n* `go_threads`\r\n* `go_goroutines`\r\n* `go_gc_duration_seconds`\r\n\r\nShould there be an option to enable this via geth flag?\r\n\r\nI see some references in [go-ethereum/metrics/debug.go](https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/master/metrics/debug.go) file, but those are not exposed via the port we use for all other metrics.",
